      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle of exceptional caliber, maintained to the highest standards of automotive preservation. This specimen exhibits an uncompromising level of care, featuring a flawless exterior finish and an interior that remains in showroom state. Mechanically, the vehicle performs with the precision and vigor of a new arrival. We invite discerning buyers to inspect this masterfully kept example, which represents a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle in truly peerless condition.",
