    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, having been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since its initial purchase. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory luster with absolutely no swirl marks, rock chips, or imperfections to speak of. Every body panel is perfectly aligned, reflecting a history of zero accidents or paintwork. Inside, the cabin still carries that new-car scent; the premium leather upholstery is supple, free of any creasing or wear, and the high-gloss trim remains scratch-free. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It has followed a rigorous maintenance schedule at authorized dealerships, with a full portfolio of service records available for review. The engine bay is immaculate, and the undercarriage is as clean as the day it rolled off the assembly line. All electronic features, from the driver-assist systems to the infotainment suite, function flawlessly. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to acquire a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives exactly as it did when it first left the showroom floor.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
